rows.label: tlk42200241_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Harula become registered citizen of
Invidia just so able to see Saffronia
tree every day.

rows.label: tlk42200241_02_msg0002
rows.name:
But...lots of troublemakers in Invidia.
Noble and mercenaries also make
life difficult, look down on others.

rows.label: tlk42200241_02_msg0003
rows.name:
After living here for a while, Harula
realize it really not pleasant place to
live for Harula.

rows.label: tlk42200241_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Would rather be in Superbia, where
everything more fancy and stylish.

rows.label: tlk42200241_02_msg0005
rows.name:
But would never be allowed after
becoming citizen of Invidia...

rows.label: tlk42200241_02_msg0006
rows.name:
Empire would also treat Harula as
spy, so probably no go anyway...
